"For example:"
msgstr "此外，如果无法获取发现端点，或者您希望减少发现端点的往返次数，可以禁用端点发现并配置相对路径值。例如："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Some OIDC providers support metadata discovery but do not return all the endpoint URLs required for the authorization code flow to complete or to support application functions, such as user logout.\n"
"To work around this limitation, you can configure the missing endpoint URL values locally, as outlined in the following example:"
msgstr "某些 OIDC 提供商虽然支持元数据发现，但不会返回完成授权码流程或支持应用程序功能（例如用户注销）所需的所有端点 URL。为解决这一限制，您可以按照以下示例所示，在本地配置缺失的端点 URL 值："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can use the same configuration to override a discovered endpoint URL if that URL is not suitable for the local Quarkus endpoint and a more specific value is required."
msgstr "如果发现的端点 URL 不适合本地 Quarkus 端点，且需要更具体的值，您可以使用相同的配置来覆盖该 URL。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For example, a provider that supports both global and application-specific end-session endpoints returns a global end-session URL such as `http://localhost:8180/oidcprovider/account/global-logout`.\n"
"This URL logs the user out of all applications the user is currently logged into."
msgstr "例如，如果某个服务提供商同时支持全局和应用程序专用的会话结束端点，则会返回一个全局会话结束 URL，例如 `http://localhost:8180/oidcprovider/account/global-logout` 。该 URL 会将用户从其当前登录的所有应用程序中注销。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "However, if the requirement is for the current application to log the user out of a specific application only, you can override the global end-session URL by setting the `quarkus.oidc.end-session-path=logout` parameter."
msgstr "不过，如果需要让当前应用程序仅将用户从特定应用程序中注销，您可以通过设置 `quarkus.oidc.end-session-path=logout` 参数来覆盖全局的结束会话 URL。"

