#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Proof Key for Code Exchange (PKCE)"
msgstr "代码交换证明密钥（PKCE）"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "link:https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc7636[Proof Key for Code Exchange] (PKCE) minimizes the risk of authorization code interception."
msgstr "link:https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc7636[“代码交换证明密钥”] （PKCE）可最大限度地降低授权码被截获的风险。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"While PKCE is of primary importance to public OIDC clients, such as SPA scripts running in a browser, it can also provide extra protection to Quarkus OIDC `web-app` applications.\n"
"With PKCE, Quarkus OIDC `web-app` applications act as confidential OIDC clients that can securely store the client secret and use it to exchange the code for the tokens."
msgstr "虽然 PKCE 对公共 OIDC 客户端（例如在浏览器中运行的 SPA 脚本）至关重要，但它也能为 Quarkus OIDC `Web 应用程序` 提供额外的保护。 借助 PKCE，Quarkus OIDC `Web` 应用程序可作为机密 OIDC 客户端，安全地存储客户端密钥，并利用该密钥交换令牌代码。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can enable PKCE for your OIDC web-app endpoint with a `quarkus.oidc.authentication.pkce-required` property and a 32-character secret that is required to encrypt the PKCE code verifier in the state cookie, as shown in the following example:"
msgstr "您可以通过设置 `quarkus.oidc.authentication.pkce-required` 属性，并提供一个 32 个字符的密钥（该密钥用于加密状态 Cookie 中的 PKCE 代码验证器），为您的 OIDC Web 应用端点启用 PKCE，如下例所示："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you already have a 32-character client secret, you do not need to set the `quarkus.oidc.authentication.state-secret` property unless you prefer to use a different secret key.\n"
"This secret will be auto-generated if it is not configured, and if fallback to the client secret is not possible when the client secret is less than 16 characters."
msgstr "如果您已经拥有一个 32 个字符的客户端密钥，则无需设置 `quarkus.oidc.authentication.state-secret` 属性，除非您希望使用另一个密钥。 如果未配置此密钥，系统将自动生成该密钥；此外，当客户端密钥长度少于 16 个字符且无法回退到客户端密钥时，系统也会自动生成该密钥。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The secret key is required to encrypt a randomly generated PKCE `code_verifier` while the user is redirected to an OIDC provider with the `code_challenge` query parameter to authenticate.\n"
"The `code_verifier` is decrypted when the user is redirected back to Quarkus and sent to the token endpoint alongside the `code`, client secret, and other parameters to complete the code exchange.\n"
"The provider will fail the code exchange if a `SHA256` digest of the `code_verifier` does not match the `code_challenge` provided during the authentication request."
msgstr "在将用户重定向至 OIDC 提供商进行身份验证时（此时会携带 `code_challenge` 查询参数），需要使用密钥对随机生成的 PKCE `code_verifier` 进行加密。 当用户被重定向回 Quarkus 时，会解密 `code_verifier` ，并将其与 `code` 、客户端密钥及其他参数一同发送至令牌端点，以完成代码交换。 如果 `code_verifier` 的 `SHA256` 摘要与身份验证请求中提供的 `code_challenge` 不匹配，提供商将判定代码交换失败。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Pushed Authorization Requests"
msgstr "推送的授权请求"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"link:https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc9126[OAuth 2.0 Pushed Authorization Requests] (PAR) allows the authorization server to authenticate the client before any user interaction happens.\n"
"It mitigates front-channel attacks by preventing malicious actors from intercepting, tampering with, or spoofing the authorization request details in the user's browser."
msgstr "link:https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc9126[OAuth 2.0 的“推送式授权请求”] （PAR）允许授权服务器在用户进行任何交互之前对客户端进行身份验证。它通过防止恶意攻击者拦截、篡改或伪造用户浏览器中的授权请求详细信息，从而减轻了前端通道攻击的风险。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can enable PAR for your OIDC web-app endpoint by setting the `quarkus.oidc.authentication.par.enabled` configuration property to `true`.\n"
"It will be enabled automatically if the OIDC metadata contains a `require_pushed_authorization_requests` property that is set to `true`."
msgstr "您可以通过将配置属性 ` `quarkus.oidc.authentication.par.enabled` ` 设置为 ``true`` ，为 OIDC Web 应用端点启用 PAR。如果 OIDC 元数据中包含一个设置为 ``true`` 的 ` `require_pushed_authorization_requests` ` 属性，则该功能将自动启用。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
