msgstr "在这种情况下，请将 `quarkus.oidc.authentication.java-script-auto-redirect` 属性设置为 `false` ，这将指示 Quarkus 返回 `499` 状态码以及包含 `OIDC` 值的 `WWW-Authenticate` 头。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The browser script must set a header to identify the current request as a JavaScript request for a `499` status code to be returned when the `quarkus.oidc.authentication.java-script-auto-redirect` property is set to `false`."
msgstr "当 `quarkus.oidc.authentication.java-script-auto-redirect` 属性设置为 `false` 时，浏览器脚本必须设置一个标头，以将当前请求标识为 JavaScript 请求，从而返回 `499` 状态码。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If the script engine sets an engine-specific request header itself, then you can register a custom `quarkus.oidc.JavaScriptRequestChecker` bean, which will inform Quarkus if the current request is a JavaScript request."
msgstr "如果脚本引擎自行设置了特定于引擎的请求头，则可以注册一个自定义的 `quarkus.oidc.JavaScriptRequestChecker` Bean，该 Bean 会告知 Quarkus 当前请求是否为 JavaScript 请求。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For example, if the JavaScript engine sets a header such as `HX-Request: true`, then you can have it checked like this:"
msgstr "例如，如果 JavaScript 引擎设置了诸如 `HX-Request: true` 之类的标头，那么你可以通过以下方式进行检查："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "After that, reload the last requested page if the status code is `499`."
msgstr "之后，如果状态码为 `499` ，则重新加载上次请求的页面。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Otherwise, you must also update the browser script to set the `X-Requested-With` header with the `JavaScript` value and reload the last requested page in case of a `499` status code."
msgstr "否则，您还必须更新浏览器脚本，将 `X-Requested-With` 头字段设置为该 `JavaScript` 值，并在出现 `499` 状态码时重新加载上次请求的页面。"

