#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Testing authentication to a separate OIDC-like server can be tricky.\n"
"Quarkus offers several options, from mocking to running a local OIDC provider."
msgstr "对独立的OIDC类服务器进行身份验证测试可能比较棘手。Quarkus提供了多种方案，从模拟到运行本地OIDC提供商不等。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
